➤HIGH WAIST & SEAMLESS: Wide waistband hugs your waist to keep them in place and prevent sagging. The seamless leggings are designed with the minimum number of seams for a more comfortable fit and increased mobility.
➤RIB-KNIT: Made from a flexible four-way knitted ribbed fabric that molds to your body. In order to make softness and comfort of the pants, we go through the washing process several times. And it provides light compression.
➤LIGHTWEIGHT & NAKED FEELING: Lightweight and ultra soft stretchy fabric creates a naked sensation, feel like a second skin without the worry of possible irritation or chaffing on the insides of your thighs.
➤WEAR IT EVERYWHERE: No need to change out of your clothes after light exercise—the seamless ribbed leggings are designed to make you look great in and outside the studio. Not suitable for high-intensity workouts, great for everyday wear or yoga.
➤WASHING INSTRUCTIONS: Separate washing is recommended. Due to the special dyeing process, these leggings may color transfer during the first washing. In addition, because of the soft nature of the product, there may be a pilling if washing with other products！
